  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Digivolving] Search your security stack. You may
    play 1 level 5 or lower Digimon card with the [Angel]/[Archangel]\_trait among
    them without paying the cost. Then, shuffle your security stack, and 1 of your
    opponent's Digimon gets -7000 DP until the end of the turn.\n[All Turns] When
    one of your Digimon with the[Angel]/[Archangel]/[Three Great Angels]\_trait would
    leave the battle area other than in battle, by trashing the top card of your
    security stack, prevent it from leaving.\n[Rule] Trait: Has the [Angel] type."
